00:54:57.120 --> 00:54:59.447
So what are some problems?

00:54:59.447 --> 00:55:01.530
Normally I get lots of
complaints in this section.

00:55:01.530 --> 00:55:03.420
You already got one
but you can answer.

00:55:03.420 --> 00:55:04.000
Yeah.

00:55:04.000 --> 00:55:07.204
AUDIENCE: They're very
