00:56:50.070 --> 00:56:51.870
bullied around the table.

00:56:51.870 --> 00:56:54.386
If someone bets and you
really want to play,

00:56:54.386 --> 00:56:56.760
you really want to stick to
your tight range, you'll fold

00:56:56.760 --> 00:56:58.860
and you'll maybe
miss out on something

00:56:58.860 --> 00:57:00.535
that you shouldn't
have depending

00:57:00.535 --> 00:57:02.160
on your position,
and things like that.

00:57:02.160 --> 00:57:02.430
PROFESSOR: OK.

00:57:02.430 --> 00:57:02.930
Good.

00:57:02.930 --> 00:57:06.560
So yes, these are
pretty tight in that it

00:57:06.560 --> 00:57:08.450
does give the other
people incentive

00:57:08.450 --> 00:57:10.100
to raise a lot
because everyone's

00:57:10.100 --> 00:57:12.350
going to be folding a lot
because you are just waiting

00:57:12.350 --> 00:57:14.260
for these really good hands.

00:57:14.260 --> 00:57:15.170
OK.

00:57:15.170 --> 00:57:17.361
That's good.

