It's roughly the same range.

00:58:10.807 --> 00:58:12.390
I think that's a
decent rule of thumb.

00:58:12.390 --> 00:58:14.460
If you just go all in
with the same range

00:58:14.460 --> 00:58:17.850
you're not going
