01:00:20.320 --> 01:00:24.250
So basically you bet big to
hope that your opponent folds.

01:00:24.250 --> 01:00:26.500
If you have a better hand,
like an average hand,

01:00:26.500 --> 01:00:28.660
often you actually
don't want to be betting

01:00:28.660 --> 01:00:29.754
