your opponent calls you

01:00:34.359 --> 01:00:36.400
when their hand is better
and you lose more money

01:00:36.400 --> 01:00:37.261
to a better hand.

01:00:37.261 --> 01:00:39.260
And your opponent folds
when their hand is worse

01:00:39.260 --> 01:00:41.590
so you're not making any
money from a worse hand.

01:00:41.590 --> 01:00:43.030
And then with your
best hands, you

01:00:43.030 --> 01:00:45.880
want to bet to try to get your
opponent to call and increase

01:00:45.880 --> 01:00:47.290
the amount that you win.

01:00:47.290 --> 01:00:48.850
And we call this value betting.

01:00:48.850 --> 01:00:52.169
